---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Work with Joshua — JSong Realty | Atlanta Buying & Selling"
  description="Buy or sell an Atlanta home with Joshua Song — Keller Williams Realty. A clear, data-first approach with vetted vendors and zero noise."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; Work with Joshua</nav>
      <span class="eyebrow">Work with Joshua</span>
      <h1>Buy or sell in Atlanta — <span class="serif-italic">without the noise.</span></h1>
      <p>A straightforward, data-first approach for both sides of the table — from first conversation to closing day.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Why work with Joshua</span>
        <h2>What you can count on.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Buying or selling a home is one of the most consequential financial decisions you'll make. Here's what working with Joshua is built around.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-grid">
        <div><strong>50+</strong><span>Atlanta transactions</span></div>
        <div><strong>$25M+</strong><span>Volume closed</span></div>
        <div><strong>&lt; 1 hr</strong><span>Avg. weekday response</span></div>
        <div><strong>9 days</strong><span>Avg. offer to ratify</span></div>
        <div><strong>5.0 ★</strong><span>Average client rating</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-muted">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split split-top panel seller-intro reveal">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Selling? Start here</span>
          <h2>What's your home worth?</h2>
          <p class="lead">Receive a thorough Comparative Market Analysis within 24 hours — grounded in recent closed sales within your submarket, prepared personally for your property.</p>
          <p class="cta-gap-sm"><span class="handwritten">— Joshua</span></p>
        </div>
        <form class="form" data-contact-form>
          <input type="hidden" name="source" value="home valuation" />
          <div class="field"><label for="s-addr">Property address</label><input id="s-addr" name="address" required /></div>
          <div class="field"><label for="s-email">Email</label><input id="s-email" type="email" name="email" required /></div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" type="submit">Request my home value</button>
          <p class="form-status" data-form-status hidden></p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Free download</span>
        <h2>The Atlanta Seller's Guide.</h2>
        <p class="lead">A working playbook covering prep priorities, pricing strategy, marketing, offer evaluation, and closing — with current submarket benchmarks and worksheets you'll actually use.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="lead-magnet reveal">
        <div>
          <h3>What's inside</h3>
          <ul class="lead-magnet-features">
            <li>Atlanta submarket cheat sheet — what's moving fast, what's sitting, and why</li>
            <li>The 7 pre-listing prep moves with the highest ROI (and the 3 to skip)</li>
            <li>How to read a CMA — and the questions to ask before agreeing on a list price</li>
            <li>Pre-listing inspection: when it's worth it, when it's not</li>
            <li>Offer-evaluation worksheet — comparing offers beyond the headline price</li>
            <li>Closing-day timeline and what your settlement statement actually means</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <form class="lead-magnet-form" data-lead-magnet-form data-guide="seller">
          <h3 style="margin-top:0;">Get the full PDF</h3>
          <p class="form-helper" style="font-size:0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Enter your email and the guide will arrive in your inbox shortly.</p>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="lm-name">Name</label>
            <input id="lm-name" name="name" required />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="lm-email">Email</label>
            <input id="lm-email" type="email" name="email" required />
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit" style="width:100%;">Send me the guide</button>
          <p class="form-status" data-form-status hidden></p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-band reveal">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light">Let's talk</span>
          <h2>Ready when you are.</h2>
          <p>Buying, selling, or simply exploring your options — begin with a complimentary 30-minute consultation, with no pressure and no obligation.</p>
        </div>
        <a class="btn btn-accent btn-lg" href="/contact/">Talk to Joshua</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
